name: モデルDEファイト(Model DE Fight)
name_original: モデルDEファイト(Model DE Fight)
description:
"Model DE Fight" (MDF) is a classic 2D fighting game.
You can play online-fighting with using informal tool.
MDF is a game made for beginners.
Currently, you can select 8 characters.
Tune-chan, Hackadoll, Iltan, Ai Kizuna, Akari Mirai, Vienne, (Cyber-Girl)Siro, Reimu Hakurei.
